{"tid":2357613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解順豐就嚟執都冇人講？","createTime":"2021-01-07T14:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T04:27:40.000Z","uid":303833,"like":122,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":66,"remark":"[gold]⚠️ 管理團隊警示：本主題已被回報為「標題誇大或與內文不符，及可能含有誤導或虛假資訊」，請各位留意。[/gold]\n警示措施說明：https://lih.kg/eobQbT","replies":[{"pid":"12b945e578cd7fafb942fbe0c97a4e42dd5d73c4","tid":2357613,"uid":303833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係標題黨<br />\n但係我真係好想同大家介紹呢個<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">優質黃色速遞App<br />\n人鏈速遞</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b85V7mN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb85V7mN.png&h=1f7fb01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地個app仲好用過順豐嗰個 勁簡單易睇<br />\n<br />\n佢地為咗整呢個app停業咗幾個月<br />\n錯過咗黃色速遞個擴張期 都係得勁少人用<br />\n<br />\n但佢地真係好有心 全部步兵都係手足嚟<br />\n<br />\n我有時都會喺IG賣嘢 雖然佢地自取點唔係好多<br />\n但真係好高汁好好用<br />\n<br />\n之前用其他速遞填google form<br />\ngoogle一死server就咩都冇曬<br />\n同埋要等好多日<br />\n<br />\n佢地仲有3日到貨保證<br />\n到貨有sms通知<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨選擇下呢個優質黃色速遞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/heEf7of.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FheEf7of.jpg&h=f636ae19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrvnNog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrvnNog.jpg&h=dd8255a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E/id1512096487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2581%259E%2Fid1512096487&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=157ef74b\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E/id1512096487</a><br />\napp link"},{"pid":"93dff6e2ae382b4385f9271de224f3beb207cb64","tid":2357613,"uid":303833,"like":0,"disl